name: Guesswhat
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess what
des:
GuessWhat will ask you a few questions about the task you have in mind but you are not sure if you want to do it.

By answering the questions, GuessWhat will let you know whether you should do the task or not and when you should do it.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
